<L>__{interior church reverend's office next morning}
<A>__{landon stands in the doorway. the reverend is wiping his glasses, his face, maybe of tears. he sees landon.}
<C>__{rev. sullivan}
<D>__{you finish?}
<C>__{landon}
<D>__{a few minutes ago. i have to ask you something.}
<A>__{long pause.}
<C>__{rev. sullivan}
<D>__{when i was seventeen, i was sent up for a year for stealing a car.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{sometimes i still feel that boy inside me and i don't like him.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{but i like you.}
<A>__{the reverend stands, offers landon his hand. landon takes it. the two men shake. allies now.}
